                            <p>I will respond with the total price; this will be based off the number of changes you request to the base template.</p>
                        </li>
                        <li>
                            <b>Price Confirmation</b>
                            <p>Confirm your acceptance with the price.</p>
                        </li>
                        <li>
                            <b>Content Creation</b>
                            <p>The creation of the website will begin.</p>
                        </li>
                    </div>
                    <div class="process-list" id="secondList">
